{"tid":863541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★why冇龍心？九西補選提名結束　合共6人報名","createTime":"2018-10-15T16:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T16:25:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1280e5d1971eff5da0e395580fa06cc3f74744c","tid":863541,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:12:53.000Z","msg":"立法會九龍西補選下月25日舉行，提名期於今午5時結束，選舉主任共接獲6份提名表格，包括今日(15日)最後一日接獲2份提名表格，而經選舉主任審核及確認獲提名人士的資格後，獲有效提名的候選人名單將於憲報刊登。<br />\n<br />\n已報名的6名參選人，包括<span style=\"color: red;\">劉小麗、馮檢基、陳凱欣、李卓人、伍迪希及曾麗文</span>，其中劉小麗日前已被選舉主任裁定提名無效，無緣參加是次選舉，理由是劉的政治立場容許港人自主命運，而香港獨立屬於選項之一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181015/bkn-20181015201132494-1015_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181015%2Fbkn-20181015201132494-1015_00822_001.html&d=MUN5g7oaV4WMM1ukgjNK%2B%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=2b0bfca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181015/bkn-20181015201132494-1015_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"58715da68cc019a10dadb687df67f7dc5d1dc9da","tid":863541,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a74880a1bb9b6f0c683510d226e383fef60c0d","tid":863541,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603790ed1deab5ee635affca35e6bbb78926d3bd","tid":863541,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"兒登仔又射唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbaeac19e0e1f6c049993bf04d1ce030bd96a874","tid":863541,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58715da68cc019a10dadb687df67f7dc5d1dc9da","tid":8635